# Day 46 – Autonomous Agent Studio

## Overview
Built an interactive Autonomous Agent Studio that demonstrates how multiple AI agents collaborate to complete a workflow through an orchestration loop.

## Features
- Multi-agent orchestration pipeline
- Planner, Executor, Evaluator, Critic, Improver, Memory Manager, and Final Reviewer
- Interactive workflow visualization
- Execution statistics dashboard
- Activity logs
- Memory management
- Score progression tracking
- Iteration history
- Responsive dark UI
- Offline HTML application

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript

## Key Learnings
- Learned how autonomous AI agents coordinate in iterative workflows.
- Explored orchestration loops and stopping conditions.
- Understood the role of planning, evaluation, feedback, and memory in agent-based systems.
- Built an interactive dashboard for monitoring agent execution.

